Step 2 — Create AWS Networking Foundation

This step creates the network where all your services will run.

Architecture
Internet
    │
Route 53
    │
Load Balancer
    │
────────────────────
Public Subnets
────────────────────
    │
NAT Gateway
    │
────────────────────
